title: Rep. Ro Khanna, D-Calif., on lawmakers demanding more Epstein files be released
description: NPR's Leila Fadel asks Democratic Congressman Ro Khanna of California about lawmakers' demands that the Justice Department release more files related to Jeffrey Epstein.
